				<div class="book-name">The First Epistle of the Blessed Apostle Paul to the Corinthians </div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"><a href="https://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/1_Cor/8058">&lt; prev</a></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 14</div>
					|<div class="next-chapter"><a href="https://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/1_Cor/8060">next &gt;</a></div>
